query:
SELECT 
  id, 
  name, 
  email,
  gerencia,
  diretoria,
  secao,
  active
FROM employees
WHERE gerencia LIKE '%Geo%'
   OR diretoria LIKE '%Geo%'
   OR secao LIKE '%Geo%'
ORDER BY name
LIMIT 20;
